Package: lbsr
Type: Package
Title: Legacy Behavioural Survey Reconstruction Toolkit
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Vito", "Bobek", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "vito.bobek@guest.arnes.si"),
    person("Tatjana", "Horvat", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides auditable project structures, evidence provenance,
    coding-book import, schema validation, sample-size diagnostics, evidence
    conflict detection, constraint classification, feasibility assessment,
    seed-controlled univariate and multivariate synthetic reconstruction,
    frequency and group calibration, reliability estimation, multidimensional
    fidelity scoring, reconstruction ensembles, assumption-sensitivity
    analysis, uncertainty summaries, reproducible report generation, and
    append-only methodological decisions for
    reconstructing legacy behavioural survey evidence. The package separates
    documentary fidelity from methodological validity and never represents
    synthetic analytical reconstructions as recovered historical respondents.
